title: [Vornavis, The Bog]
description: The path crests a ridge here before descending to the west, south, and southeast.  To the west, the swamp is thick and active, with birds flying about the treetops and insects swarming along the water.  To the south and southeast, the plant life has turned brown and gray, as if struggling for life.
